query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk t) NoMergeJoin(k mk t ci) NoNestLoop(ci k mk t n) */ select min(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
min(n.name) AS actor_name,
min(t.title) AS hero_movie
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder-in-title',
'violence',
'tv-special',
'revenge',
'blood',
'marvel-cinematic-universe',
'magnet',
'female-nudity')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2007
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id;
